abstract: College Football Roundup; Mississippi State defeats North Carolina State, 51-28; other college football scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Dak Prescott threw for 380 yards and four touchdowns as Mississippi State routed North Carolina State in the Belk Bowl in Charlotte, N.C.

headline.main: Dak Prescott’s Big Day Propels Mississippi State
headline.print_headline: Big Game by Prescott Propels Bulldogs
